  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091230" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">一种定时语音提示录放装置,由电子时钟、整形电路、语音驱动器、音乐集成片、语音电路和扬声器构成。使用时,在电子时钟上设定时间,到时电子时钟发出双极性脉冲信号,再经过语音驱动器触发音乐集成片,通过扬声器播发音乐,经过延时,触发语音电路,通过扬声器播放语音,语音事先录制在语音电路中,延时的时间与音乐的播放时间相同。本实用新型可以定时提醒人们去做某些事情,先放音乐再播放语音可引起人们的注意,并且不感觉突然。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091230" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The utility model relates to a timing voice-prompt recording and playing device, which is composed of an electronic clock, a rectifying circuit, a voice drive, a music integrated chip, a voice circuit and a loudspeaker. During use, time is preset on the electronic clock. When time is up, the electronic clock sends out the double-pole pulse signal and then passes the voice drive to trigger the music integrated ship, passes the loudspeaker to play the music, passed the time delay to trigger the voice circuit and passes the loudspeaker to play the voice. The voice is in advance recorded into the voice circuit and the time delay is the same with the playing time. The utility model can remind people to do something. Music playing before playing the voice can arouse attention, without the abrupt feeling.</p>
  </abstract>
